snippet.title: SUPER ROBOT WARS Y - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Robot Wars Y is coming to PlayStation 5, Nintendo Switch, and STEAM in 2025!
Wishlist Now: https://www.bandainamcoent.com/games/super-robot-wars-y

Super Robot Wars is a grid-based tactical combat RPG that brings units and pilots from a variety of anime together to battle their mutual foes. 
 
Rise, Unite, and Triumph!

Follow Bandai Namco Entertainment: 
X (Twitter): https://twitter.com/BandaiNamcoUS 
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@bandainamcous
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/bandainamcous
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/BandaiNamcoUS
Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/bandainamcous
